How can I help you?

**List of categories:**
1. Moderation
2. Fun
3. Misc
4. Music

To navigate through the categories, type **./help (number)**
actions.name: Set Embed Description

actions.message:
**Bot moderation features**:

**./ban**: Ban a specified user. (Usage: **./ban (user)**)
**./newrole**: Creates a new role. The role is named "new role" by default. (Usage: **./newrole**)
**./kick**: Kicks a specified user. (Usage: **./kick (user)**)
**./nuke**: Bulk-deletes a specified amount of messages (Usage: **./nuke (number of messages)**)
actions.name: Set Embed Description

actions.message:
**Bot fun features:**

**./level**: Shows you your activity level on the server (Usage: **./level**)
**./8ball**: 8ball is a ball of wisdom. Who knows the answers you get will reflect the truth? (Usage: **./8ball (question)**)
**./ping**: Specially created to annoy users. Pings a specified user 15 times. (Usage: **./ping (user)**)
**./nn**: Changes a specified user's nickname to "nn dog". (Usage: **./nn (user)**)
**./memes**: Gives you a certified, high quality meme. (Usage: **./memes**)
**./random**: Gives you a random number between 0-1 (Includes decimals. Usage: **./random**)
**./dick**: Shows you your dick size. Legend says what's posted by the bot reflects the truth (Usage: **./dick**)
**./iq**: Shows your IQ, time to accept the truth that you're just dumb (Usage **./iq**)
**./roast**: Roasts someone with some 🔥 insults! (Usage: **./roast @[someone]**)
**./pfp**: Sends you the pfp of a mentioned member (Usage: **./pfp @[someone]**)
**./trash**: Turns your friend into a trash (If they aren't one in the first place :wink: ) (Usage: **./trash @[someone]**)

Please note that the bot will give you notifications on someone's level up **if you change one of your channel's name into "level"**.
actions.name: Set Embed Description

actions.message:
**Bot misc features:**

**./god**: Shows you the faith and the belief of invalidbot and humanity in general. (Usage: **./god**)
**./botusers**: Shows you how many users does the bot serve. (Usage: **./botusers**)
**./server**: Shows you the link to invalidbot's official discord server! (Usage: **./server**)
actions.name: Set Embed Description

actions.message:
**Bot music features:**

**./play**: Plays a music based on youtube search results (Usage: **./play [search term]**)
**./skip**: Skips the currently playing song to the nest queue (Note that this only works if there IS another song in the queue)
**./clear**: Clears the current queue (Usage: **./clear**)
**./setvol**: Sets the volume of music bot (Usage: **./setvol [number 1-100]**)
**./dc or ./disconnect**: Disconnects bot from voice channel (Useful if you want to change voice channels, as the bot can only play in one channel)
